    Switch_touch_text:
      "A smart switch that doesn't require changes to your lighting or wiring. No neutral wire is needed. Just replace your traditional switch and enjoy wide functionality — remote control via app, scheduled or timer-based switching, and voice control via Yandex Station.",
    Switch_touch_color_text: "(Colors: White, Gold, Gray, Black)",
    Switch_keyboard_text_1:
      "The switch housing fits standard electrical boxes. The front panel is made of high-quality plastic with control keys and LED status indicators.",
    Switch_keyboard_text_2:
      "Direct connection to Yandex Zigbee — connect Roximo devices directly to a Zigbee-enabled Station or Yandex hub.",
    Switch_keyboard_color_text: "(Colors: White, Gold, Bronze, Gray, Black)",
    Switch_roller_touch_text:
      "Smart Wi-Fi curtain switch for electric curtains, roller blinds, shutters. Works like a regular wall switch but allows control from a mobile app. Installs in place of a traditional switch and connects via Wi-Fi.",
    Socket_buildIn_text:
      "Remotely turn off an iron or curling iron, turn on a heater or AC on your way home, set light schedules for plants or aquariums, turn on decorations via voice and more. With energy monitoring, track consumption in the app and see which devices are currently in use.",
    Socket_buildIn_color_text: "(Colors: White, Gold, Gray, Black)",
    Dimmer_touch_text:
      "A smart dimmer is the perfect solution for controlling light intensity in your smart home. Adjust brightness levels via app or the device's touch panel.",
    Dimmer_Yandex_text:
      "The Yandex smart dimmer helps you fine-tune your home lighting — from bright and energizing to soft and relaxing. Only works with dimmable bulbs. Requires a neutral wire and fits a standard round wall box.",
    Relay_dimmer_text:
      "Zigbee dimmer relay is an innovative Smart Home device that lets you control lighting via phone app or voice. Compact mini design fits most switch and outlet boxes.",
    Slug_Yandex_text:
      "Works with Matter protocol — easily connects to your smart home. Scenes continue to function even without internet. Compact and minimal, fits most outlets. Control remotely, set schedules, receive status notifications.",
    Slug_Tuya_text:
      "Matter-enabled Smart Plug - 16A. Works with Alice voice assistant. Just scan the QR code to connect — no hub needed!",
    Slug_Roximo_text:
      "Control it via app and track energy usage from anywhere in the world. Set automation based on time, countdown, cycles, weather, sunrise/sunset, or location. Yandex Alice integration enables voice control.",
    Slug_Smartlife_text_1:
      "Control the plug remotely by phone or voice within any smart home ecosystem. Timer setup is available.",
    Slug_Smartlife_text_2:
      "An essential device for remote control of appliances like lights, garlands, kettles, heaters, TVs, fans, humidifiers, etc. Displays real-time energy usage. Create smart scenarios and group with other devices.",
    Relay_Yandex_text:
      "The Yandex smart relay is a compact device that turns regular switches into part of a smart home. Installs behind existing switches and connects via Zigbee 3.0.",
    Button_Yandex_text:
      "Battery-powered and can be used as a doorbell or multifunction button. Easy to place anywhere — doorframe or nightstand. Link with devices and set up routines via Yandex Home. When used as a doorbell, it sends signals to your Station and app. Or use silent mode for no interruptions.",
    Smart_Din_63A_text_1:
      "Tuya Zigbee DIN rail smart breaker with Alice voice support lets you control lights, sockets, and appliances without extra wiring. Use the Smart Life app or voice. Supports 220V with real-time energy monitoring. Easy to install with DIN rail. Yandex Smart Home compatible.",
    Smart_Din_63A_text_2:
      "This 63A Zigbee DIN breaker is a reliable solution for automating home tasks and saving energy. Suitable for high-power appliances in both home and industrial use.",
    Smart_Din_40A_text:
      "DIN rail circuit breaker 40A for 220V 50/60Hz networks. Zigbee-compatible and controlled via Tuya or SmartLife app. Integrates with popular voice assistants.",
    Smart_Din_Moes_16A_text_1:
      "MOES ZCB‑SC‑1P16 smart breaker offers modern electrical management for your home or office. Compact, modular, and reliable — supports overload and short-circuit protection, plus remote control via smartphone.",
    Smart_Din_Moes_16A_text_2:
      "Supports 230V and 16A, ideal for home or commercial use. Provides power on/off, device sync, and safety protections.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_1:
      "Smart ZigBee breaker with 63A overload and short-circuit protection. Controls lighting and appliances via wall switches or 'YaSmart' app. Compatible with Yandex Alice, Google Assistant, Alexa.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_2: "Manual control with button.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_3: "Internet control without subscription.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_4: "Weekly/daily schedule for auto on/off.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_5: "Countdown timer.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_63A_text_6: "Push notification on schedule execution.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_80A_text_1:
      "Smart Zigbee breaker — ideal for managing lighting and electrical appliances. Features overload and short-circuit protection for safety and reliability.",
    Smart_Din_Tuya_80A_text_2:
      "Includes remote switching, switch control, manual button, online monitoring, scheduling, countdown timer, push notifications, and full protection.",
