    "LED-Strip_Yandex_text":
      "The Yandex LED strip YNDX‑00544, complete with controller and power adapter, operates reliably via switch, voice commands, and the “Home with Alice” app. This model supports control via Bluetooth, Wi‑Fi and Matter protocols. The latter is convenient when your home includes smart devices from different manufacturers. Each meter of the strip contains 24 LEDs with a light output of 250 lm, making YNDX‑00544 suitable for long assemblies on ceilings and walls. Short segments provide less light but still work well for decorative purposes. The 3‑meter strip with IP65 splash and dust protection is suitable for outdoor and bathroom installation.",
    "Cable_LED-Strip_Yandex_text":
      "The extension cable for the Yandex LED strip YNDX‑00547 is suitable for extending assemblies with 24 diodes per meter. Its tightly braided jacket fully protects contacts from dust and moisture, allowing outdoor or bathroom installation. The 250 lm brightness is sufficient for ambient or decorative lighting and zoning. YNDX‑00547 supports neutral white light as well as RGB tones and effects. Control is supported via simple switch, controller, mobile app, and voice commands.",
    "LED-Strip_Kojimo_text":
      "The smart Wi‑Fi RGB LED strip KOJIMA offers adjustable light output from 70 to 800 lumens with low power consumption. The mobile app is adapted for most iOS and Android devices. You can easily control brightness and color, set dynamic scenes, schedule on/off via timer, group strips with one tap, and use voice control with Yandex Alice.",
    "LED-Strip_Roximo_text_1":
      "The smart addressable Wi‑Fi LED garland ROXIMO SFCL01‑L, 10 meters long, is part of the Roximo smart home ecosystem. The strip is a key element for holiday decoration. Thanks to IP67 water protection (control unit is IP44), you can use it indoors and outdoors.",
    "LED-Strip_Roximo_text_2":
      "In the Roximo app you will find buttons and various functions for the smart garland: drawing – selecting color schemes + creating your own; color music + custom creations; setting scenes + custom ones; timer settings and other adjustments.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_1:
      "Two lighting zones: The fixture includes a main light source with a wide color temperature range (2700K‑6500K) for adjustable white light and a side light source with 16 million colors to create a vibrant ambiance.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_2:
      "High brightness: The main light source offers a maximum output of 3450 lumens, providing ample illumination for your space.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_3:
      "Control via app: You can adjust color temperature, brightness, and RGB effects through the Aqara Home app.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_4: "Dimmable: The lamp can be dimmed, allowing you to set brightness to your needs.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_5: "Long lifetime: The LED light source has a rated life of 50,000 hours, ensuring durability.",
    Lamp_Aqara_text_6:
      "Stylish design: The Aqara Ceiling Light T1M features a slim, modern design that complements various interiors.",
    Night_light_RGB_text_1:
      "Smart LED Wi‑Fi RGB night lamp/table lamp KOJIMA with adjustable output from 70 to 400 lumens and low power consumption. You can easily control brightness and color, set dynamic scenes, schedule on/off via timer, group lamps with one tap, and use voice control via Yandex Alice.",
    Night_light_RGB_text_2: "- 16 million RGB colors",
    Night_light_RGB_text_3: "- Color temperature from 2700K to 5700K",
    Night_light_RGB_text_4: "- Housing material: ABS plastic",
    Night_light_RGB_text_5: "- Height 18 cm, Diameter 10 cm, Weight 385 g",
    "Control_LED-Strip_text":
      "Dimmer controller for smart home, works with Alice. Allows you to adjust LED strip brightness via voice assistant or automation scenarios.",
    "Control_LED-Strip_RGB_text":
      "We present our new Wi‑Fi controller — a compact and stylish solution that will bring new life to your lighting system and make your home truly smart! Full integration with popular 'Smart Home' systems: Yandex Alice, Amazon Alexa, and Google Home. Simply say: “Alice, turn on the holiday lighting!” Enjoy over 100 modes from smooth color transitions to dynamic light effects. With a sleek design and compact size in classic white, this controller blends seamlessly into your home.",
    Bulb_dimmable: "Dimmable bulb",
    Bulb_E27_9_Yandex_filamentous_text:
      "The ability to adjust color temperature from 2700 to 6500K and brightness lets you create warm soft lighting for a romantic evening or cool bright light for productive work.",
    Bulb_E27_9_Yandex_text:
      "The ability to adjust color temperature from 2700 to 6500K and brightness lets you create warm soft lighting for a romantic evening or cool bright light for productive work.",
    Bulb_Yandex_RGB_text:
      "The ability to change the light color allows different lighting scenes to match your mood or task: bright violet light for a kid’s room, blue for immersion while gaming, or Party mode when you have guests.",
