    Cornice_Tuya_text_1:
      "The electric motor supports wireless communication via the Zigbee protocol, which allows smart home scenarios to run without needing a direct internet or WiFi connection. This is one of the key advantages of Zigbee technology. You can control it via remote control, through an app, or via the Alice voice assistant.",
    Cornice_Tuya_text_2: "Package includes: telescopic track, electric motor, remote control",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_1:
      "A great solution for curtains — the Xiaomi Aqara Smart Curtain Controller CD‑M01D Zigbee electric track. With it, you can easily schedule sunrise and sunset times in your room, apartment, or home, and adjust lighting levels with a single tap. Beyond fully opening or closing curtains, it allows partial opening and setting timers for auto open/close at specified times.",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_2: "Control of electric curtains:",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_3: "Start and stop curtains using smartphone via the Xiaomi Mi Home or Aqara Home app",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_4:
      "Manual control of curtains: Gently pull the curtain and the system will take over to fully open or close it",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_5: "Manual operation of curtains when power is unavailable",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_6: "Smooth start/stop operation",
    Cornice_Aqara_text_7: "Control via Yandex Alice voice assistant",
    Cornice_Roximo_text_1:
      "This is a complete kit containing everything needed for easy installation, including a high‑power smart motor of 45 W, allowing you to use curtains weighing up to 50 kg and lengths of up to 12 meters.",
    Cornice_Roximo_text_2:
      "The track can be used with center opening or with opening in one direction (left or right). You can control the track from anywhere via the dedicated app, add smart scenes and schedules based on time, countdowns, weather, sunrise/sunset, your location, and more.",
    Cornice_Roximo_text_3:
      "Package contents: smart motor; track; belt; 2 gliders; roller kit (8 pcs per meter); remote control; motor mounting + cover; ceiling mounting bracket",
    Cornice_Roll_59_text:
      "The Aqara smart motor for roller blinds is designed for controlling rolling curtains, partitions, or projection screens. You can manage the blinds via smartphone, the included remote control, or voice assistants like Alice.",
    Motor_Rolling_Aqara_text_1:
      "Universal use: Fits most types of curtains or blinds with shafts from 35 to 70 mm in diameter",
    Motor_Rolling_Aqara_text_2:
      "Elegant design: The body is made of white plastic to blend into any interior. Scheduling: Set automatic opens/closes based on time of day, sunrise/sunset, or other events.",
    Motor_Rolling_Aqara_text_3: "Manual control: You can duplicate control via a button on the device",
    Motor_Rolling_Aqara_text_4:
      "Overload protection: Built‑in motor protection prevents damage if the mechanism is blocked",
    Motor_Rolling_Aqara_text_5: "Quiet operation: Enjoy near‑silent motor performance",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_1:
      "Beyond full open or close, you can partially open to a set distance and schedule automatic open/close at a given time.",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_2: "In addition to mobile control, you can use a wireless button.",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_3: "Convenience and aesthetics:",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_4: "Quiet operation of motor and mechanisms",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_5: "Motor can be placed on either side of the track: left or right",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_6: "The motor is hidden inside the tube",
    Cornice_Rolling_Aqara_text_7:
      "Package contents: aluminum tube, mounting bracket kit, adapter set, ZNGZDJ11LM motor",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_1: "Control of Roman shades:",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_2: "Start and stop via smartphone using the Xiaomi Mi Home app",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_3: "Start and stop via a button or switch",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_4: "Operation when internet is down: scenarios run locally within home network",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_5: "Control via Yandex Alice voice assistant",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_6: "Maximum shade height — 6 meters",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_7: "Maximum shade weight — 15‑17 kg",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_8: "Convenience and aesthetics:",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_9: "Quiet motor and mechanism operation",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_10: "Motor can be installed on either side of the track: left or right",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_11: "Motor is concealed inside the tube",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_12: "Profile quality: anodized aluminum, powder‑coated",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_13: "Package contents:",
    Cornice_Roller_Shade_Aqara_text_14:
      "Aluminum track, rope pulleys (2–3 per meter), octagonal shaft, adapter set, bottom bar, motor, fiberglass inserts, plastic rings.",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_track_text_1:
      "Turn ordinary curtains into smart ones — it’s easier than ever. The device fits almost any type of track.",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_track_text_2: "Mounts to the track and hooks. One device per curtain.",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_track_text_3: "Hook length (from bottom of hook to track): 16–25 mm",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_track_text_4: "Track width: 10 mm",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_rod_text_1:
      "This smart drive is designed for automatic opening and closing of curtains mounted on rod‑type tracks. It allows remote control via smartphone, scheduling, or voice commands, integrating into popular smart home ecosystems.",
    Driver_Curtain_Aqara_rod_text_2:
      "Durable casing and quality materials ensure long life. Aqara smart drive is a step toward full home automation, comfort, and energy efficiency.",
    Motor_Roller_Aqara_text:
      "A device for automatic curtain control. Make your blinds, roller shades, or chain‑controlled curtains smart. Easy to install and battery powered. It can be controlled via smartphone, voice assistants, automations, and wireless switches. Opens or closes curtains fully or to a set percentage.",
    Close_water_Aqara: "Aqara Water Shut-off Actuator",
