    Close_water_Aqara_text:
      "The intelligent actuator Aqara T1‑VC‑X01E is a Zigbee‑based valve control device suitable for both smart (wireless) and manual control of plumbing systems. It can link with water leak sensors to detect risks, send alerts and trigger shutoff, protecting property and ensuring safety.",
    Close_water_text:
      "Electric actuator for shutting off water/gas, valve drive with Alice support — an excellent solution for your smart home. It lets you control water and gas shutoff in your house, enhancing safety and efficiency.",
    Smart_Ball_Valve_DN25_text_1:
      "Electric ball valve 1 inch, 220 V — the guardian of your repair safety and peace of mind!",
    Smart_Ball_Valve_DN25_text_2:
      "When a leak occurs, the valve automatically shuts off the water. Works best paired with a leak sensor. Upon signal reception, it closes the valve. A push notification arrives within 2 seconds in the mobile app. Controlled via Alice voice assistant.",
    Smart_Ball_Valve_DN20_text_1: "Electric ball valve 3/4 inch, 220 V — safeguarding your repairs and peace of mind!",
    Smart_Ball_Valve_DN20_text_2:
      "On leak detection, the valve auto shuts the water off. Most effective when used with a leak sensor. Receives signal and closes the valve. Push alert in 2 seconds via app. Controlled via Alice.",
    Control_heater_Aqara_text:
      "Aqara Smart Radiator Thermostat E1 regulates radiator temperature. Installs in place of standard M30×1.5 mm head. Use with a temperature sensor for comfort in any room. Comes with adapters for compatibility with most radiator valves. Also includes antifreeze protection to activate heating in freezing conditions.",
    Control_heater_Beok_text_1:
      "Thanks to the built‑in thermostat, auto on/off, display and remote control, users can easily manage indoor temperature without leaving home.",
    Control_heater_Beok_text_2:
      "Additional features like child lock and smartphone control simplify voice control. Heating devices connect to the thermostat, ensuring efficient heat distribution throughout the home.",
    Control_floor_Electsmart_black_text:
      "This thermostat fits nearly every electric underfloor heating up to 3500 W, as well as hydronic floors with manifolds and actuators, typically of the “normally closed” type.",
    Control_floor_Welrok_white_text_1:
      "Welrok smart thermostat for managing underfloor heating via smartphone or computer. Its app feature saves money by reducing heating when no one is home.",
    Control_floor_Welrok_white_text_2:
      "When geofencing is enabled, Welrok uses user location to lower or shut off heating when you leave a set radius, and restore comfortable temperature when you return. Adjust heating settings via Yandex Alice.",
    Control_floor_Welrok_white_text_3:
      "Welrok Wi-Fi thermostats can be integrated into your Smart Home via MQTT and HTTP API.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_1:
      "The Celtic DS M3hgb smart thermostat is a modern solution for home temperature management, offering comfort and energy savings.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_2: "Features:",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_3: "- Alice voice control — voice commands for your convenience.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_4: "- Touch display — intuitive interface for easy operation.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_5: "- Programmable mode — temperature scheduling by time of day.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_6: "- Max load 3500 W — suitable for most heating systems.",
    Control_floor_Celtic_text_7: "- Temperature range control 5 °C to 50 °C — ideal year‑round.",
    Control_boiler_Bugatti_text_1:
      "The Federica Bugatti Wi‑Fi boiler control module is a modern solution for smart heating control. It enables remote control and automation of your heating system to make your home more comfortable and efficient.",
    Control_boiler_Bugatti_text_2:
      "This module combines advanced technology, ease of use and high reliability. You get full control over your home heating, save resources and maintain a comfortable microclimate at all times.",
    Control_boiler_Beok_text_1:
      "A Wi-Fi thermostat for gas and electric boilers — a modern functional device that maintains the required room temperature.",
    Control_boiler_Beok_text_2:
      "This thermostat handles gas and electric heating boilers (Baxi, Buderus, Bosch, Protherm, Wolf, Vaillant, Viessmann, Zota, Ariston, Navien, Mizudo, Evan, Thermex, Electro, Kiturami, Rinnai, etc.). You can control the boiler remotely from anywhere, making it an indispensable home assistant. The unit features touch control and adjustable temperature settings. With built‑in sensor, it measures actual room temperature and activates accordingly.",
    Boiler_THERMEX_Sonne_grey_text:
      "The THERMEX Sonne 12 Wi‑Fi Grey wall electric boiler is a reliable, efficient solution for heating your home or cottage. Its 12 kW output can heat areas up to 120 m², providing comfort during cold seasons. Wall mounting saves space, and its elegant grey design fits any interior. The Wi‑Fi function lets you control it remotely via smartphone or integrate it into a smart home (e.g. with Alice). With included installation kit and user guide, setup is simple.",
    Boiler_THERMEX_Cometa_text:
      "The THERMEX Cometa 12‑24 Wi‑Fi electric dual‑circuit boiler is a modern solution for heating and hot water in your home or cottage. With 24 kW, it efficiently serves areas up to 240 m². The dual circuits ensure both climate control and hot water supply. Controlled via intuitive panel or Wi‑Fi for remote control and automation with voice assistants like Alice.",
    Boiler_THERMEX_Boss_text:
      "The THERMEX Boss 12 Wi‑Fi White wall electric boiler is a reliable and efficient heating solution. With 12 kW power, it's ideal for spaces up to 120 m². Wall mounted to save space, its white design suits any decor. Equipped with Wi‑Fi for remote control via smartphone or smart home integration. The included kit and manual make installation straightforward.",
    Boiler_THERMEX_Sonne_white_text:
      "The THERMEX Sonne 12 Wi‑Fi White wall electric boiler offers dependable efficient heating for your home or cottage. It supports up to 120 m², features Wi‑Fi control, fits elegantly into interiors, and includes all installation accessories and a manual.",
    Heating_thermostat_ZONT_text_1:
      "The ZONT H‑1V NEW heating thermostat is designed to maintain comfortable indoor temperatures. It controls your boiler from anywhere via web portal or ZONT mobile app. It supports 10 custom heating modes, schedule programming, outdoor temperature compensation (OTC), and time‑based operation. Logs and stores an event history.",
    Heating_thermostat_ZONT_text_2:
      "Backup battery included: in case of power outage, the device remains online for up to 12 hours and continues relaying data from connected wired sensors.",
    Heating_thermostat_ZONT_text_3: "Mounts on a DIN rail",
