    Smart_mirror_text_1:
      "A wall-mounted illuminated mirror is not only a functional interior element but also a stylish addition to your bathroom. An illuminated mirror in the bathroom is an excellent choice for creating a cozy atmosphere. A wall-mounted illuminated mirror in the hallway becomes a stylish accent in your home.",
    Smart_mirror_text_2:
      "Choose lighting to match your mood: buy a large neutral 4500K mirror for the hallway to easily apply makeup, or a 6000K cold‑light mirror to help with concentration. For the bathroom, a 3000K warm light mirror will let you feel summer sunshine. If choosing is hard, opt for a 3‑in‑1 light (3000K, 4500K, 6000K) or get an RGB light version with a million colors.",
    Camera_Yandex: "Yandex Video Surveillance Camera",
