    Camera_4G_Roximo: "Roximo 4G Smart Outdoor Rotating Camera",
    Camera_street_rotary_Roximo: "Roximo Smart Outdoor Rotating Camera",
    Camera_Yandex_text_1:
      "The YNDX-00582GRY surveillance camera is a perfect choice for home and cottage. It is Yandex's first smart camera with a modern design and high-quality Wi-Fi video surveillance. It integrates with the Alisa ecosystem, features a 103º viewing angle and a 350º rotating mechanism, allowing you to capture every detail. It activates recording when motion or sound is detected and enables night vision in darkness.",
    Camera_Yandex_text_2:
      "You can monitor the stream via the app or TV Station and share access with relatives. The camera notifies you of any activity and can disable recording if needed.",
    Camera_Yandex_text_3: "Interfaces: USB, Wi-Fi, microSD card support.",
    Camera_Yandex_text_4: "Features: motion detector, privacy mode, IP20 protection rating.",
    Camera_Yandex_text_5:
      "Additional functions: built-in microphone, video streaming to smartphone, voice control via Yandex Station.",
    Camera_street_Roximo_text_1:
      "The camera can be controlled via a special mobile app to view everything happening at your home online. Video can be recorded on an SD card or cloud storage for later viewing. When the security function is used, the camera automatically records and saves video upon motion detection.",
    Camera_street_Roximo_text_2: "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication.",
    Camera_street_Roximo_text_3:
      "Package contents: manual – 1 pc; mount – 1 pc; power adapter – 1 pc; smart camera – 1 pc",
    Camera_rotary_Roximo_text_1:
      "The IP camera has a rotation function and can view the space at a full 360 degrees. The kit includes a special mount, and the camera can be fixed to a wall or ceiling, with image rotation available in camera settings.",
    Camera_rotary_Roximo_text_2:
      "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication, video nanny.",
    Camera_rotary_Roximo_text_3:
      "Package contents: USB cable – 1 pc; power adapter – 1 pc; manual – 1 pc; smart camera – 1 pc; mounting kit – 1 pc",
    Camera_Roximo_text_1:
      "The camera is housed in a case designed for installation on a special rotating stand. The stand platform can also be mounted to a wall or ceiling, and the image can be flipped in the camera settings.",
    Camera_Roximo_text_2: "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication, video nanny.",
    Camera_Roximo_text_3:
      "Package contents: 3M tape – 1 pc; USB cable – 1 pc; power adapter – 1 pc; manual – 1 pc; smart camera – 1 pc",
    Camera_E27_Roximo_text_1:
      "Thanks to the E27 power adapter, the camera can be installed by screwing it in place of a light bulb. The IP camera has a rotation function and can view the space at a full 360 degrees. The kit includes a special mount, and the camera can be fixed to a wall or ceiling, with image rotation available in camera settings.",
    Camera_E27_Roximo_text_2: "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication, video nanny.",
    Camera_E27_Roximo_text_3:
      "Package contents: USB cable – 1 pc; power adapter – 1 pc; manual – 1 pc; mounting kit – 1 pc; E27 power adapter – 1 pc; smart camera – 1 pc",
    Camera_4G_Roximo_text_1:
      "The presence of a SIM card slot and support for 4G communication standard allow installing the camera anywhere without the need for internet connection for remote monitoring. Video can be recorded on an SD card or cloud storage for later viewing. When using the security function, the camera automatically records and saves video upon motion detection.",
    Camera_4G_Roximo_text_2:
      "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication, patrol mode, return to standby position.",
    Camera_4G_Roximo_text_3: "Package contents: manual – 1 pc; mount – 1 pc; power adapter – 1 pc; smart camera – 1 pc",
    Camera_street_rotary_Roximo_text_1:
      "The Roximo RHC202 smart outdoor rotating camera is one of the devices in the Roximo smart home ecosystem.",
    Camera_street_rotary_Roximo_text_2:
      "The camera has a rotation function and can view the space at a full 360 degrees. The kit includes a special mount, and the camera can be fixed to a wall or ceiling, with image rotation available in camera settings. When using the security function, the camera automatically records and saves video upon motion detection.",
    Camera_street_rotary_Roximo_text_3:
      "Available features: night mode, motion detection, two-way communication, patrol mode, return to standby position.",
