    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30: "Xiaomi Smart Door Lock E30",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100: "Aqara A100 Lock",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100: "Aqara Electro-Mechanical Door Lock D100",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100: "Aqara Electro-Mechanical Door Lock N100",
    Smart_Window: "RoboArm Smart Window Opener",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_1:
      "The Xiaomi Smart Door Lock is a modern solution to secure your home with a wide range of features and a high level of protection.",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_2: "9 unlocking methods:",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_3: "— AI fingerprint scanner (accuracy 99.29%, speed 0.5 sec)",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_4: "— Permanent and one-time passwords",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_5: "— Bluetooth via smartphone",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_6: "— Mechanical key",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_7: "— NFC cards (sold separately)",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_8: "— Unlocking via Xiaomi smartphones, watches, and bracelets, Gizmochina",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_9: "Six-level security system:",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_10: "— Class C lock cylinder",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_11: "— Protection against burglary and tampering",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_12: "— Door ajar sensor notifies the user if the door is not fully closed",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_13: "— Integration with Mi Home and HyperOS",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_text_14: "Emergency power supply via Type-C (5 V, 0.5 A)",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_1: "Camera",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_2:
      "The AI-powered intelligent detection system automatically activates video recording when someone lingers near your door, instantly sending a notification to your smartphone. You can monitor events in real-time from anywhere and take appropriate actions.",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_3: "Unlocking",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_4:
      "The lock offers 9 different unlocking methods, including an AI fingerprint scanner with 99.29% accuracy and 0.5 second unlock speed. The app allows you to create temporary or permanent keys for family members, friends, or service staff, providing flexibility and control over home access.",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_5: "Protection",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_6:
      "The device is equipped with a class C cylinder, making it resistant to burglary. The six-level lock protection system ensures a high level of security. The built-in door ajar sensor with notification feature provides an additional security layer.",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_7: "Power Supply",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_8:
      "The lock has two power sources: main powered by 4 AA batteries and backup powered by a 5000mAh lithium battery. In case the batteries run out, you can use emergency power supply through the Type-C port to open the door.",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_9: "Mi Home App",
    Smart_Door_Xiaomi_E30_text_10:
      "Thanks to Bluetooth 5.0 and Wi-Fi, the lock easily integrates into your home network, allowing control from anywhere in the world. Use the Mi Home app to manage access remotely, track open/close history, and receive notifications about unauthorized entry attempts.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_1:
      "The Aqara Door Lock A100 Zigbee Edition has a fingerprint-resistant aluminum body. It alerts about burglary attempts and multiple incorrect password entries. The device has a hidden keypad — to activate it, you need to touch the sensor panel.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_2: "Unlocking Methods",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_3: "Remotely via the Aqara Home app",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_4: "Fingerprint",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_5: "Permanent password",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_6: "One-time password",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_7: "Temporary password",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_8: "Mechanical key",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_9: "NFC tag",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_A100_text_10:
      "If the batteries run out, you can still open the lock with a mechanical key or power it via the Type-C port.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_1:
      "This is a smart door lock that ensures the security and convenience of your home. It is equipped with many features that allow you to lock and unlock the door using various methods, as well as monitor activity and receive notifications.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_2: "Unlock Methods:",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_3:
      "Fingerprint: D100 can store up to 20 unique fingerprints, providing quick and secure access.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_4:
      "Password: Use permanent or temporary passwords for access, convenient for guests or cleaning staff.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_5: "NFC: Unlock the lock by touching an NFC card or an NFC-enabled smartphone.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_6:
      "Mechanical key: Use in unforeseen situations when electronic methods are unavailable.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_7:
      "Remote access: Lock and unlock remotely via the Aqara Home or Apple HomeKit app from anywhere.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_8: "Security Features:",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_9:
      "Burglary detection: Receive notifications if someone attempts to break into your door.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_10:
      "Incorrect password attempts: The lock automatically locks after several incorrect password entries.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_11:
      "“Away from home” mode: Activate this mode, and the lock will automatically lock after the door closes.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_12:
      "Two-factor authentication: Add an extra security layer using two-factor authentication when accessing the lock remotely.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_13: "Other Features:",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_14: "Activity log: View lock usage history to see who opened the door and when.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_15: "Voice control: Use Siri or Google Assistant for voice command control of the lock.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_16:
      "Automation: Create automation scenarios for the lock to interact with other smart devices in your home.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_D100_text_17:
      "Long battery life: The lock is powered by a lithium-ion battery lasting up to 1 year on a single charge. Backup power: The lock has a USB-C port for charging in case the battery runs out.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100_text_1:
      "The device can be installed on wooden and steel doors with a panel thickness of 40 to 80 mm.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100_text_2: "Unlocking Methods",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100_text_3:
      "The lock supports unlocking via fingerprint, password, NFC card, temporary password, HomeKit, or emergency key.",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100_text_4: "Smart doorbell",
    Smart_Door_Aqara_N100_text_5:
      "The internal lock panel has a speaker that plays a doorbell melody when the external panel button is pressed. If you don't want to use the bell, set automation differently — for example, send a notification to your smartphone or turn on the hallway light when the button is pressed. This is convenient if you don't want to wake family members or disturb pets.",
    Smart_Window_text_1:
      "The window actuator is perfect for creating maximum comfort – remote ventilation of rooms, automatic humidity level regulation, and fresh air access.",
    Smart_Window_text_2:
      "The opening width is 15-20 cm, which is sufficient; the opening size can also be adjusted in percentages.",
    Smart_Window_text_3:
      "Attention: The device does not have obstacle protection! If you forget to physically open the window's locking handle and activate the actuator, it is likely to break down.",
